      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s seriously in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been meticulously cared for and is ready for its next adventure, this is the one. Can't wait for you to take it for a spin!",
