    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in collector-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis is structurally immaculate, with documented subframe reinforcement and a recent rod bearing service ensuring mechanical longevity. Power is routed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory M Variable Differential Lock. The exterior retains its factory depth with zero oxidation, while the suspension kinematics remain tight and responsive. A truly turn-key specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Clean title. Full service history. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 42500.0,
